### JetBrains HTTP Client format
### See: https://www.jetbrains.com/help/idea/http-client-in-product-code-editor.html

#@host = localhost:8080
@host = lea-analyzer.default.svc.cluster.local

### Liveness
GET http://{{host}}/healthz

### Readyness
GET http://{{host}}/readyz

### Prometheus metrics
GET http://{{host}}/metrics

### Analyze events
POST http://{{host}}/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Are there any harmful or malicious executions? What are the implications?",
  "time_range": {
    "start": "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
    "end": "2027-01-01T00:00:00Z"
  },
  "max_events": 50
}
